{"type": "article", "id": 28319, "title": "监测情绪的智能手环", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-17T06:40:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021645257MyRLEtTKVlmzosZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>昨天我们推荐过一款专门监测自闭症儿童焦虑情况的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28263.html\">手环</a>，伦敦的设计工作室 VINAYA 同样把设计方向聚焦在了人们的精神健康上，推出了这款名为 ZENTA 的智能手环。手环采用了先进的传感技术，可以监测到各种身体参数。配合上地理位置和日程安排等信息，它会记录下你一段时间以来的情绪以及压力变化，并且根据不同的情况提出建议，避免陷入紧张的状态当中。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/zenta-for-your-emotional-physical-wellbeing--2#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 149 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164522Nx2YAVeWb3GIfCLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66883117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164523JLiGIrYnzxeTDjA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84354839\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021645230YITKvBckCOEmrnN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164524c5mspGVAbdatHhIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21061644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}